==反响==
===收视率===
《我们的孩子，我们自己》首播当晚在美国一共有约1112万户家庭观看，于18至49岁年龄段所获得的收视率为4.2 / 10%<ref name="tvratings">{{cite web|last=Seidman |first=Robert |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/01/13/wednesday-final-ratings-the-middle-adjusted-down-off-the-map-adjusted-up/78550/ |title=Wednesday Final Ratings: ‘The Middle’ Adjusted Down; ‘Off The Map’ Adjusted Up |publisher=Tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com |date=2011-01-13 |accessdate=2013-07-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009124245/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/01/13/wednesday-final-ratings-the-middle-adjusted-down-off-the-map-adjusted-up/78550/ |archivedate=2012-10-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。这意味着全美所有18-49岁人群中有4.2%观看了该节目，而在当时所有观看电视的18-49岁观众群中则有10%观看本集。根据尼尔森媒体调查的数据，这是星期三收视率最高的节目<ref name="tvratings" />。和上一集《[[拖累邻居|拖累邻居]]》相比这个数字略有降低，可能是因为播出时间推迟的影响<ref name="tvratings"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/01/06/tv-ratings-wednesday-abc-comedies-human-target-l-live-to-dance-peoples-choice-awards-tumble/77452/ |title=TV Ratings Wednesday: ABC Comedies, 'Human Target,' 'L&O:SVU' Up; 'Live To Dance,' 'People's Choice Awards,' Tumble |author=Gorman, Bill |date=2011-01-06 |work=''TVbythenumbres.zap2it.com |accessdate=2013-07-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009012736/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/01/06/tv-ratings-wednesday-abc-comedies-human-target-l-live-to-dance-peoples-choice-awards-tumble/77452/ |archivedate=2012-10-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。不过这一集节目还是成为美国广播公司该周收视率第二高的节目，仅次于《[[实习医生格蕾|实习医生格蕾]]》，在所有电视台中名列第7位<ref>{{cite web|last=Seidman |first=Robert |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/01/19/tv-ratings-broadcast-top-25-nfl-playoffs-ncis-greys-anatomy-modern-family-and-60-minutes-lead-week-17-viewing/79313 |title=TV Ratings Broadcast Top 25: NFL Playoffs NCIS, Grey’s Anatomy, Modern Family and 60 Minutes Lead Week 17 Viewing |publisher=Tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com |date=2007-08-28 |accessdate=2013-07-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019144315/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/201